snippet.textDisplay:
Do I regret not drafting a QB for 30-plus years? Of course. This franchise could have done great things if they showed the same courage for 20 or so years that they showed when they picked Mahomes. Would any of those QB's have been as unique and special as Mahomes? No way. But it STILL goes to show that if you want to win championships, you can't trot Trent Dilfer( or worse )out there every season and expect to have a realistic shot.
That said, if you have to wait that long to finally pull the trigger, Mahomes is the very best prize you could possibly ask for.
